    "didyouknow": [
        {
            "title": "Enhanced Phone Validation Now Built into Clearout Form Guard",
            "body": "<p>We&#x2019;ve <strong>upgraded the phone validation layer within Clearout Form Guard</strong> to improve real-time validation accuracy and reduce junk or risky submissions before they enter your CRM.</p><p><strong>&#xA0;What&#x2019;s Improved:</strong></p><ul><li>Enhanced mobile vs VoIP vs landline classification</li><li>Reduced false positives and grey responses</li><li>More consistent validation across global networks</li></ul><p><strong>&#xA0;What This Means for You:</strong></p><ul><li>Higher lead quality at the point of capture</li><li>Cleaner CRM data without manual filtering</li><li>Better sales team efficiency</li></ul><p>These <strong>improvements are automatically applied to all forms </strong>protected by Clearout Form Guard &#x2014; <strong>no configuration changes required.</strong></p>",
            "url": "https://changelog.clearout.io/enhanced-phone-validation-now-built-into-clearout-form-guard-2XvX2w"
        },
        {
            "title": "Introducing Auto Credit Replenishment – Never Run Out of Credits Again!",
            "body": "<p>We&#x2019;ve launched a new automated credit top-up feature to help you stay uninterrupted when using Clearout.</p><p>With Auto Credit Replenishment, your account will automatically add credits when your credit balance gets low - so your API workflows, Form Guard, bulk validations, and integrations continue running without any disruption or manual intervention.</p><h3>Key Benefits:</h3><ul><li>&#x2705; Zero downtime &#x2013; your operations never stop due to insufficient credits</li><li>&#x2705; Fully automated &#x2013; you choose the threshold and top-up amount</li><li>&#x2705; Complete control &#x2013; enable, disable, or adjust anytime</li><li>&#x2705; Instant invoices &amp; transparent billing</li></ul><p>You can enable this feature now from your&#xA0;<a href=\"https://app.clearout.io/account/manage-plans?utm_source=announcement&amp;utm_medium=inapp&amp;utm_campaign=auto_credit_replishment\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Plans</strong></a> section.</p><p>Try it today and experience uninterrupted credit usage with full automation!</p>",
            "url": "https://changelog.clearout.io/introducing-auto-credit-replenishment---never-run-out-of-credits-again-13mq9a"
        },
        {
            "title": "Cyber Monday is now LIVE!",
            "body": "<p><strong>Thank you for an incredible Black Friday response &#x1F64F;</strong><br>For everyone who missed it or reached out asking for another chance &#x2192; here it is.</p><p><strong>30% OFF on 100K and above credits, use the code at checkout to save big.</strong></p><p>This is the perfect time to start 2026 strong &#x2192; Add credits &amp; save:</p><ul><li>Prepare for Q1 outreach &amp; onboarding</li><li>Enhance deliverability &amp; sender reputation</li><li>Avoid credit shortages during peak campaigns</li></ul><p><strong>Use code &#x2192; </strong><a href=\"https://app.clearout.io/pricing/?showbuynow=true&amp;product_id=673f2521231fd5f807a4068b&amp;quantity=100000&amp;coupon_code=CYBER30&amp;utm_source=announcement&amp;utm_medium=inapp&amp;utm_campaign=cybermonday2025\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>CYBER30</strong></a><br>&#x23F3; <strong>Ends December 5 (00:00 UTC)</strong></p>",
            "url": "https://changelog.clearout.io/cyber-monday-is-now-live-24VK8w"
        },
        {
            "title": "🚨 12 Hours Left – Final Black Friday Countdown",
            "body": "<p>Secure the <strong>biggest discount of Black Friday 2025.</strong></p><p>This year, we&#x2019;ve opened the sale to:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://app.clearout.io/pricing?utm_source=blackfriday&amp;utm_medium=landingpage&amp;utm_campaign=co_black_friday_launch_2025_12hrs_annual\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Annual Subscriptions</strong></a><strong> (up to 50% OFF)</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://app.clearout.io/pricing?billing=payg&amp;utm_source=blackfriday&amp;utm_medium=landingpage&amp;utm_campaign=co_black_friday_launch_2025_12hrs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discounted PAYG credits</strong></a></li><li><strong>Best pricing for API &amp; Form Guard usage</strong></li><li><strong>Optimized deliverability for all of 2026</strong></li></ul><p>&#x23F3; <strong>When the clock hits zero, this sale disappears until next year.</strong></p><p>&#x1F449; <a href=\"https://app.clearout.io/pricing?billing=payg&amp;utm_source=blackfriday&amp;utm_medium=landingpage&amp;utm_campaign=co_black_friday_launch_2025_12hrs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Get My Offer Now</strong></a></p>",
            "url": "https://changelog.clearout.io/12-hours-left---final-black-friday-countdown-PIQKY"
        },
        {
            "title": "Black Friday 2025 is live – and it’s our biggest yet.",
            "body": "<p>For the first time ever, <strong>Annual Subscriptions</strong> are in the Black Friday sale with <strong>up to 50% OFF</strong> &#x2013; along with discounted <strong>PAYG credits</strong>.</p><p>What&#x2019;s on the table?<br>&#x2705; Lowest pricing ever on Annual plans<br>&#x2705; Pay-As-You-Go credits on Black Friday slabs<br>&#x2705; Perfect for uninterrupted validation all through 2026<br>&#x2705; Best value for Form Guard, APIs, campaigns, and scaling teams</p><p>The sale is now open.<br>Lock in your discounts before it ends <span style=\"text-align:start;\">&#x2192;</span> <strong>once-a-year pricing</strong>, no fluff, just savings.</p><p><a href=\"https://clearout.m-pages.com/CI2rqb/black-friday-sale-2025?utm_source=inapp&amp;utm_medium=announcement&amp;utm_campaign=co_black_friday_2025\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Grab Your Black Friday Deal &#x2192;</strong></a></p>",
